{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_06_02",
  "title": "成宮すず 2話 エンドレスクリスマスですわ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月スト・クリスマスライブの後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― After Moon Tempest's Christmas Live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（今日のクリスマスライブは凄い盛り上がりだったな）\n（琴乃の誕生日サプライズもうまくいったし……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Today's Christmas Live was incredibly exciting‚ wasn't it?）\n（Kotono's birthday surprise went well too…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（すずも満足しているはずだ。……そう思って）\n（夜更かししていないか、様子を見に来てみたが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（ I think Suzu should be satisfied……so）\n（I came to check if she's stayed up late……）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ぽけー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*Zoning out",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "すず？　あんなに楽しみにしていたクリスマスなのに\nどうして気の抜けた顔なんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu? It's finally Christmas‚\nand you look so unenthusiastic. Why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、聞いて下さいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "[user]-san‚ please listen!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "今日のクリスマスライブ、月ストの一員として\n私もステージに立ったのですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "During today's Christmas Live‚ as a member of Moon Tempest‚\nI also stood on the stage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5299.999999999997,
          "startTime": 39.3333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasstage-00-night",
      "startTime": 37.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasstage-00-night",
      "startTime": 38.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "みなさーん、盛り上がってますわねー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ it's so exciting‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasstage-00-night",
      "startTime": 42.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスは街中がキラキラしていて\n光り輝くトップアイドルの私にぴったりの日ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Christmas makes the whole city sparkle‚ and\nshining brightly like me who's perfect for a top idol",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasstage-00-night",
      "startTime": 50.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "私が聖夜を笑顔で溢れる夜にしてみせます\n今日という日を忘れられない思い出にしますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll make this Holy Night overflow with smiles.\nI'll make today a memorable day!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6500,
          "startTime": 60.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasstage-00-night",
      "startTime": 58.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "最高のクリスマスの始まりですわー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's the beginning of the best Christmas!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_night",
      "startTime": 63.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すず達のパフォーマンスで\n会場のボルテージは一気に上がっていたな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The venue's energy shot up\nthanks to Suzu and the others' performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスを私達と過ごしたいと思ってくれる人が\nあんなにいると分かって、私も興奮しましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got excited too‚ knowing that so many people wanted\nto spend Christmas with us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "それでパフォーマンスにも熱が入って\n最高潮に盛り上がったところで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ as the excitement reached\nits peak on stage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "ステージ上で琴乃の誕生日サプライズが\n行われたのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-san's birthday surprise was\ncarried out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasstage-00-night",
      "startTime": 89.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasstage-00-night",
      "startTime": 89.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみなさんと一緒に誕生日をお祝い出来て\n素敵なサプライズになりましたわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being able to celebrate her birthday with our fans\nwas a fantastic surprise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6966.666666700007,
          "startTime": 101.2
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_xmaslivestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "xmasstage-00-night",
      "startTime": 97.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "こんなに沢山の人が琴乃を祝福してくれて\nとっても感動的ですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's so touching to see\nso many people blessing Kotono-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_night",
      "startTime": 104.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "俺も会場で見ていたが\nみんなのサプライズ、凄く良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was watching at the venue too‚ and\neveryone's surprise was really great.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "ありがたいですわ\n琴乃も喜んでくれて素晴らしいお祝いになりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. Kotono-san was delighted so\nit turned out to be a wonderful celebration.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "その後、ライブが終わって\nみんなは寮に帰ったんだよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the live‚\neveryone went back to the dorm‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "はい、私達は達成感に浸りながら\n寮でクリスマスパーティーを始めたのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ we started a Christmas party at the dorm‚\nimmersed in a sense of accomplishment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "メリークリスマス！　食べて、喋って、歌って、笑って\n最高のクリスマスパーティーにしますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Merry Christmas! Eating‚ talking‚ singing‚ laughing -\nwe'll make it the best Christmas party!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "（友達と過ごす初めてのクリスマス……。始まる前から）\n（ドキドキソワソワして、ワクワクが止まらなくて……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（My first Christmas spent with friends… ）\n（I was so excited before it even started…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "（私が飾り付けしたツリーをみんなが褒めてくれました）\n（みんなで食べる料理がとても美味しく感じます）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Everyone praised the tree I decorated）\n（and the food we all ate tasted so great.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "（ライブで疲れているはずなのに）\n（幸せ過ぎて笑顔が止まりませんわ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Despite being tired from the live‚）\n（I couldn't stop smiling with happiness!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "今夜のパーティーは、胸の奥が熱くなるような\n幸福な時間でした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tonight's party was a time of happiness\nthat warmed my heart…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "今のところ充実したクリスマスとしか思えないが\nそれでどうして気の抜けた顔をしていたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It sounds like a so satisfying Christmas‚\nso why did you look so deflated?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "確かにクリスマスパーティーは楽しかったですわ\nとってもとっても楽しかったのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Christmas party was indeed fun‚\nvery‚ very fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "それはもう楽しくて……あんまり楽し過ぎて……\n私、燃え尽きてしまいました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So fun that…\nI've burnt out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz022.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと楽しみにしていた沢山のイベントが\n今日一日で全て終わってしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All the events I was looking forward to\nended in just one day…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz023.m4a",
      "text": "私はこの先、何を楽しみに生きていけばいいのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What am I supposed to look forward to now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "燃え尽きたってそういう意味か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Burnout‚ is that what you meant?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスが終わっても、気持ちを切り替えて\n明日からまた頑張ればいいじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Christmas is over‚ but just switch your mood\nand carry on",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 215.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz024.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスが終わっても？\n……いいえ、クリスマスは終わりません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Christmas is over?\n…No‚ Christmas isn't over.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz025.m4a",
      "text": "この幸せな時間を終わらせはしません！\nパーティーをしている限りクリスマスは続くのですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't let this happy time end!\nAs long as I'm having a party‚ Christmas continues.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "クリスマスパーティーはもう終わってるだろ？\nすずの他に誰もいないじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Christmas party is finished‚ isn't it?\nYou're the only one left.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz026.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、みなさんお疲れで\n部屋に戻って眠ってしまいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "True‚ everyone was tired and\nwent back to their rooms to sleep.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 241.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "すずもそろそろ休んだ方が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should probably rest soon too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz027.m4a",
      "text": "ですが！　私はまだまだ終わりません！\n私だけでもクリスマスを延長するのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But! I'm not done yet!\nI'll extend Christmas by myself!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 250.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz028.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、今からクリスマス二次会を始めましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's start the second part of the Christmas party!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 254.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "二次会って、パーティーをするにしても\nすずの他に誰もいないじゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A second part‚ but there's nobody else\nexcept for Suzu to party with‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz029.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんがいるではありませんか！\nさあ、私と一緒に二次会をやりますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're here‚ aren't you‚ {user}-san?\nCome on‚ join me for the second part of the party!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 267.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz030.m4a",
      "text": "今夜は寝かせませんわ！\n私達が眠らなければクリスマスは永遠に続くのですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't let you sleep tonight!\nAs long as we don't sleep‚ Christmas will go on forever.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 274.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "やれやれ……\nすずが満足するまで付き合うしかなさそうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh boy… Looks like I have no choice\nbut to keep Suzu company until she's satisfied.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 281.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_06_02-suz031.m4a",
      "text": "私が眠らないように話し相手になりなさい！\nクリスマスの夜を私と二人で過ごすのですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Be my conversation partner to keep me awake!\nSpend this Christmas night with me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 289.4,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}